## Getting started

1. Fill in `CHARTER.md` (the upfront gate) before other work.
2. Fill the command placeholders in `AGENTS.md`.
3. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and set real values (never commit `.env`).
4. `just` lists the available tasks.

## Foundation updates

```
just foundation-update
```

Pulls the latest groundwork release in via Copier's 3-way merge. Requires a
clean working tree.
